gomodel:SYNGO_2586  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" , "Rationale: Fig.1: \"Localization of Slitrk1 at the synapse\"\n- \"These analyses revealed that a portion of Slitrk1 protein is found in synaptic membrane fractions (Fig. 1d)\"\n- \"Note that Slitrk1 is detected in synaptic fractions including P2, P2* and the postsynaptic densities (PSD).\"\n\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: \"PSD fractionation was performed on hippocampi isolated from 3-4 week old mouse brain as described\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0593-3443" ;
